## Notes
- The project uses `requestAnimationFrame` and `THREE.Clock` for smooth animations.
- Planet distances and sizes are scaled for visibility, not astronomical accuracy.
- Tested on modern browsers (Chrome, Firefox, Safari) for performance and compatibility.